1.0.0

# Semantic Versioning Format: MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH

## Version History

### 1.0.0 (Current) - 2024-05-11
- Initial release
- Firebase authentication (email/password and Google Sign-In)
- Approval request management system
- Real-time notifications (foreground, background, and closed app)
- Python client tools for testing

## Guidelines for Version Updates

1. MAJOR version (1.x.x) - Incompatible API changes or significant redesigns
2. MINOR version (x.1.x) - New functionality added in a backward compatible manner
3. PATCH version (x.x.1) - Backward compatible bug fixes or minor improvements 